{"tid":1215551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解到今時今日 對住班黑警都可以咁和平","createTime":"2019-06-13T07:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T07:58:50.000Z","uid":23878,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8161ee194fb0b8e01a8e44e50ef4c2d84d2242","tid":1215551,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:30:33.000Z","msg":"呢幾日睇網上 睇現場直播 同埋發夢 都覺得香港人好和平.<br />\n掉野又話唔好.隔離post重要無掉磚，好和平為榮。<br />\n點解你地咁撚忍得？睇完啲狗點濫權到咁都咁和平。<br />\n義士俾人十幾個黑警禁係地下打，女人俾人非禮，近距離開槍，一字排開咁企係到俾人搜身，記者表明身份照打，多撚到數唔曬。 <br />\n我有時發得香港人俾黑警更無血性，係咪唔燒到自己到就當無事發生？食催淚彈唔嬲咩？用把口大叫黑警死全家就有用？ 啲黑警當你傻仔咋。<br />\n我真係希望你地可以醒一醒，俾少少怒火。咁叫示弱，唔係叫示威。當然我都明唔係個個都咁勇，我相信有足夠嘅情報同撤退路線，根本唔會俾捉到。<br />\n<br />\n如果叫我出黎做箭靶，不如算鳩數。咁樣真係爭取唔到啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我愛谷桃<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kiNnvZt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkiNnvZt.png&h=8d61a039&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvHOrxP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvHOrxP.png&h=2451c0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有緣再見"},{"pid":"dbfb32ed6ccf4e81ce3d1aa4be787b79b2314cb2","tid":1215551,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:33:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dc5751b98901c3be2885441a131f4ec355711085","tid":1215551,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"是勇者不必怕<br />\n希望勇果班 good luck"},{"pid":"8fce0aedce3356914ab30989923f25b090f18ba2","tid":1215551,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:35:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"814bdf242a941f7e2369d4a573d83cd53eb37d2d","tid":1215551,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:37:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03d1567f319471261506761863812d394e20feda","tid":1215551,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:51:35.000Z",